  "tutMorphWelcomeTitle": "Welcome to Morph",
  "tutMorphWelcomeBody": "This is the most different place you'll reach. Morph bends everything you're used to — but don't worry, we'll work through it together, step by step. Ready when you are.",
  "tutMorphOriginalTitle": "First, the basics",
  "tutMorphOriginalBody": "You place and capture pawns just like in Original. If you haven't learned that yet, drop by there first.",
  "tutMorphMysteryTitle": "But winning…",
  "tutMorphMysteryBody": "In this mode you'll need to do something else to win…",
  "tutMorphShapesTitle": "Four pawns, one shape",
