  "tutMorphZTitle": "A diagonal Z",
  "tutMorphZBody": "Place your pawn on the glowing square and complete a slanted Z.",
  "tutMorphMirrorTitle": "The mirror counts too",
  "tutMorphMirrorBody": "A shape's mirror image wins just like the shape itself. A flipped L is still an L.",
  "tutMorphLTitle": "A mirrored L",
  "tutMorphLBody": "Finally: place on the glowing square and complete a mirrored L.",
  "tutMorphDoneTitle": "That's Morph!",
